title 主流程活动图
start
:进入 buildRiskPlan();
:withDefaults() 归一化 riskPreferences;
:计算 availableCashPct / concentration;
:汇总 sectorExposure -> correlationWarnings;
:按 market state 计算 regimeMultiplier;
:推导 portfolioRiskBudgetPct / maxSingleNamePct / defaultProbePct;
if (RISK_OFF?) then (是)
  :封禁 ADD;\n必要时封禁 PROBE;
endif
if (availableCashPct < defaultProbePct?) then (是)
  :封禁 ADD;
endif
if (所有 timing cards 都不是 ADD/PROBE?) then (是)
  :封禁 ADD;
endif
:组装 notes / warnings / blockedActions;
:返回 PortfolioRiskPlan;
stop
